Will China lag behind if it does not build such a warship?
With the recent major naval powers in the world has announced the construction plan of new frigates, as if overnight frigates have become the focus of the Navy of major powers, first Japan in the 2018 annual defense budget to determine the purchase of two new frigates, so that the Japanese DEX frigate plan finally had a substantial breakthrough, and then the United States Lockheed Martin recently announced the latest plan of the United States FFG frigate plan, then China's new frigates where to go?
With the launch of a new Type 054A frigate at the end of 2017, it marks that the 054A frigate has built up to 29 ships, has been close to the sum of the 053H series frigates, and from the first 054A in 2006 to the present, the construction of the 054A has been 12 years, even in the world, the construction of such a large number of high-performance general-purpose frigates, in addition to China, only the United States in the 1970s and 1980s construction of the "Perry" class frigate can be compared.
And why build so many 054As is simple: it is affordable, easy to use, and complementary to the Navy’s debts of years.
054A frigate with high cost performance and good combat effectiveness for many years to get the favor of the Chinese Navy, its displacement of about 4,000 tons, equipped with a 76 mm main gun, 32 units of sea red flag-16 and fish-8 anti-submarine missile co-launched vertical system, 8 eagles 83 and a straight-9 helicopter, although it began to build in 2006, the design time is a kind of ship, but its combat effectiveness even today is not too bad, looking at the world's frigates can reach the level.
But after all, this is a type of 21st century design of the ship, the weapon configuration is set aside, its power system and electronic radar equipment and the current world mainstream frigates compared to the existing gap, such as Europe's same type of frigate has been equipped with full electric propulsion, small multi-function phased array radar, large-scale helicopter deck, it is also time to develop a new model.
So how China's new frigates should develop is directly related to its future positioning and the strategic approach of our Chinese navy.
The future development of the Chinese navy will be completely blue water navy, and the future will also be to the ocean, with the rapid deployment of areas with close interests in China, showing the existence of force, if necessary, to have a strong combat power to ensure that China's vital interests in the region will not be damaged, so it seems that the new Hu Weijiang will be towards large-scale and ocean-going development.
Looking at the positioning of the new frigate in the future Chinese naval sequence, the future Chinese Navy should be similar to the U.S. Navy, in addition to the necessary offshore defense ships, other main ships will form an aircraft carrier battle group or amphibious assault ship strike group according to the needs of the situation.
The role of the new frigate in the future carrier battle group should act as the anti-submarine main force and the positioning of the hollow and near-regional release, in the amphibious assault ship strike group should act as a escort ship class, then according to the demand for the new frigate must have a strong anti-submarine capability and good medium-range area release capability.
Based on the above positioning, you can boldly imagine the general appearance of domestic frigates in the future.
First of all, the displacement relative to the current 054A frigate will have a substantial increase, it is estimated that the displacement of the new frigate will reach about 5000-6000 tons; the power system will use a QC280 improved gas turbine and two diesel engines composed of an integrated electric propulsion system, the maximum speed is expected to reach about 30 knots, the endurance will also increase significantly; as for the weapon configuration 76 mm main gun and 1130 near fire cannon should be retained, but will increase a red flag 10 launch system, the main gun should have a 32-48 unit.An 8-16 unit of large vertical system should be installed for launching Eagle Strike 18 and a new cruise missile; the hangar and shutdown platform will also increase, reaching the parking and storage of two 10-ton helicopters; for the electronic radar system, the high-end system should be equipped with small four-sided fixed phased array radar based on the 346A, and the low combination can use a multifunctional rotary phased array radar similar to the European frigate.
In this way, the overall level of the new frigate will reach the current world-class level, even if it is not more than the United States FFG.
Of course, the above concept is only the author's conjecture about the domestic new frigate, how can we only wait until the new frigate is launched to find out, let us look forward to it together.
